## Welcome Page
pages.welcome.title                     = Before you register for VAT
pages.welcome.heading                   = Before you register for VAT
pages.welcome.heading.register          = To register for VAT you'll need:
pages.welcome.bullet.details.person     = details of the person registering your company for VAT (for example, National Insurance number)
pages.welcome.bullet.details.company    = details of what your company does
pages.welcome.bullet.details.sales      = your company''s total estimated sales that are subject to VAT (or <a href="https://www.gov.uk/vat-registration/calculate-turnover">VAT taxable turnover</a>) for the next 12 months

